---

<section id='about' class='about-section'>
  <div class='container'>
    <div class='about-grid'>
      <!-- Bio Column -->
      <div class='bio-col reveal'>
        <h2 class='section-title'>
          Values & <span class='highlight'>Experience</span>
        </h2>
        <p class='bio-text'>
          I'm a software engineer specializing in high-performance web
          applications. From healthcare logistics to fintech, I've built
          solutions that drive real business impact.
        </p>
        <p class='bio-text'>
          Currently leading web engineering at ShortPoint, I've previously
          shipped production apps in healthcare and banking. I care deeply
          about accessibility, performance, and building software that makes a
          difference.
        </p>
        <a
          target='_blank'
          href='a-temitayo-salaudeen-resume.pdf'
          class='btn'
          data-text='Download Resume'>Download Resume</a
        >
      </div>

      <!-- Experience Column -->
      <div class='experience-col'>
        <div class='experience-card reveal'>
          <div class='card-header'>
            <h3>Lead Web Engineer</h3>
            <span class='year'>2024 - Present</span>
          </div>
          <span class='company'>ShortPoint</span>
          <p>
            Leading web platform optimization and migration to custom-built
            solutions. Increased website performance by 200% and lead
            generation by 30%.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='experience-card reveal delay-100'>
          <div class='card-header'>
            <h3>Senior Frontend Engineer</h3>
            <span class='year'>2024 - 2025</span>
          </div>
          <span class='company'>Peerless</span>
          <p>
            Frontend Team Lead for a micro-frontend core banking application.
            Built permission-based access controls and platform-wide services
            for all teams.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class='experience-card reveal delay-200'>
          <div class='card-header'>
            <h3>Web & Mobile Engineer</h3>
            <span class='year'>2023 - 2024</span>
          </div>
          <span class='company'>LifeBank</span>
          <p>
            Built internal web apps and React Native mobile apps for a
            healthcare logistics company to manage medical supply orders.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Background subtle decoration */
  .about-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle,
      var(--color-primary-dim) 0%,
      transparent 70%
    );
    opacity: 0.1;
    filter: blur(50px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .bio-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 500px;
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-bg-accent);
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  /* Experience Column */
  .experience-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* Replicating the 'Frontend' card style */
  .experience-card {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-bg-accent);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      border-color 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* .experience-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--color-primary-dim);
  } */

  .experience-card .deco-corner {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    opacity: 0.1;
    border-radius: 100% 0 0 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .experience-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-main);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .year {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .company {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .experience-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #ccc;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1; /* ensure text is above deco */
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
